###############################################
# 9. WORKFLOW SIMULATION
###############################################

### WORKFLOW 1: Initial Screening Process
# Step 1: Start screening for all cabang
GET {{baseUrl}}/penyesuaian/screening?cabang=All&periode={{periode}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Step 2: Check summary after screening
GET {{baseUrl}}/penyesuaian/summary?cabang=All&periode={{periode}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Step 3: Get records to review issues (sorted by highest SESUAI)
GET {{baseUrl}}/penyesuaian?periode={{periode}}&sortColumn=SESUAI&sortOrder=DESC&limit=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### WORKFLOW 2: Single Store Refresh (UI Button Click)
# User sees data in table, clicks refresh button on specific row
# Step 1: Refresh specific store
GET {{baseUrl}}/penyesuaian/screening?kdtk={{kdtk}}&periode={{periode}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Step 2: Verify updated data for that store
GET {{baseUrl}}/penyesuaian?kdtk={{kdtk}}&periode={{periode}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### WORKFLOW 3: Re-screening to Resolve Issues
# After store fixes issues, re-run screening
# Step 1: Re-run screening for same periode
GET {{baseUrl}}/penyesuaian/screening?cabang={{cabang}}&periode={{periode}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Step 2: Compare summary (resolved records moved to RECID='1', not shown)
GET {{baseUrl}}/penyesuaian/summary?cabang={{cabang}}&periode={{periode}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Step 3: Verify remaining issues (only RECID='*' shown)
GET {{baseUrl}}/penyesuaian?periode={{periode}}&cabang={{cabang}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### WORKFLOW 4: Store-by-Store Resolution
# Process for handling multiple stores with issues
# Step 1: Get list of stores with issues
GET {{baseUrl}}/penyesuaian?periode={{periode}}&cabang={{cabang}}&limit=100
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Step 2: Refresh first store
GET {{baseUrl}}/penyesuaian/screening?kdtk=TW75&periode={{periode}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Step 3: Refresh second store
GET {{baseUrl}}/penyesuaian/screening?kdtk=T001&periode={{periode}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Step 4: Check updated summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/penyesuaian/summary?cabang={{cabang}}&periode={{periode}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

